title: #92Noon! Lavelle/Leber/Reeve/Davis
description: Draft conversation begins the show, followed by a quick check-in on Lavelle. Leber in studio all 10a hour! Cheryl Reeve is on as the WNBA draft is tomorrow night, and NFL Network's Charles Davis breaks down players and offers opinions for the draft!
